<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Counter Offer Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #FF9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .offer-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #FF9800;
        }
        .amounts {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .amount-box {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .counter-offer {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #FF9800;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .action-needed {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px solid #FF9800;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ü§ù Counter Offer Received</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{buyerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>The seller has made a counter offer for your winning bid! They would like to negotiate the final price.</p>
        
        <div class="offer-details">
            <h3>Auction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Item:</strong> {{auctionTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> #{{auctionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="amounts">
            <div class="amount-box">
                <h4>Your Original Bid</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #666;">${{originalBid}}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="amount-box">
                <h4>Counter Offer</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF9800; font-weight: bold;">${{counterOfferAmount}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-needed">
            <h3>‚è∞ Action Required</h3>
            <p>Please log in to your account to respond to this counter offer. You can either:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Accept</strong> the counter offer and proceed with the transaction</li>
                <li><strong>Reject</strong> the counter offer and decline the purchase</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> The seller is waiting for your response!</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>This is a great opportunity to negotiate and potentially secure the item you wanted. Please consider the seller's counter offer carefully.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AuctionBid Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from AuctionBid Platform</p>
        <p>Log in to your account to respond to this counter offer</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
